{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775842710661,"sessionID":"ses_2878747b9ffeIS08VEA5449r4J","part":{"id":"prt_d78794199001fr5LJLMd925x38","messageID":"msg_d787934560012m54CDAZxtdyV8","sessionID":"ses_2878747b9ffeIS08VEA5449r4J","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_36bbaa7494464e31ba37d2bf","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-005/CHANGE.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-005/CHANGE.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-005 — Sandbox 创建处理器\n2: \n3: ## Summary\n4: Implement sandbox creation processor in the workloadmanager module.\n5: \n6: ## Module\n7: `pkg/workloadmanager`\n8: \n9: ## Language\n10: Go\n11: \n12: ## Size\n13: M\n14: \n15: ## Status\n16: Draft\n17: \n18: ## Description\n19: This change implements the sandbox creation processor responsible for:\n20: - Initializing sandbox environments for workloads\n21: - Configuring isolation boundaries\n22: - Managing resource allocation for sandboxes\n23: \n24: ## Files to Change\n25: - `pkg/workloadmanager/sandbox_processor.go` (new)\n26: - `pkg/workloadmanager/sandbox_processor_test.go` (new)\n27: \n28: ## Dependencies\n29: - None\n30: \n31: ## Risks\n32: - Medium complexity - requires careful handling of isolation boundaries\n\n(End of file - total 32 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-005 — Sandbox 创建处理器\n\n## Summary\nImplement sandbox creation processor in the workloadmanager module.\n\n## Module\n`pkg/workloadmanager`\n\n## Language\nGo\n\n## Size\nM\n\n## Status\nDraft\n\n## Description\nThis change implements the sandbox creation processor responsible for:\n- Initializing sandbox environments for workloads","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-005/CHANGE.md","time":{"star